title: Intelly Tech
author: Intelly Tech
content: We at Intelly are looking for a new community builder/manager,What we are looking for?We are looking for individuals who are experienced in community building.We are looking for individuals who are fluent English speakers.We are looking for individuals who are enthusiastic and knowledgeable about crypto and real estate.We are looking for individuals who can work hand in hand with our social media and marketing team to help our project and community to grow.If you see all these things in you, Then apply and become part of the Intelly Team.For the application please fill out this form: https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdKKwMzbw3qZRqrkZIqjgjazb5qozTrxuYZKsqHwE_K4HRLNA/viewformFor more information about intelly, you can check our official website: https://intelly.tech/
